{
  "stem": "26022.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We lived in a residential section, so nothing much happened out there, until or unless a specific incident took place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, that brings up a specific incident.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] lived on Billrothstrasse, which is a fairly large [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] main street in the suburbs.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean on the outskirts.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Of course, it still was in the city limits, towards the Vienna woods.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there are two trolley lines going through that-- the 38 and the 39.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And a few blocks beyond the house where we lived, they separate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The 38 goes here, and the 39 goes there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They all go to the-- basically, to the Vienna woods, but different-- have the terminal at different places, not far from there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in between, is a triangular island.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And on one side, we had a piece of property that my parents had hoped to build their retirement home on in years to come.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was 50.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother was 47 when all this happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was far in the future, but we had a little weekend house there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was walking from where we still lived to that weekend house, passed that island, and saw [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a bunch of hoodlums-- three or four-- attacking an old Jew-- a bearded Jew-- and pulling his beard out so that the blood ran over his chin with the flesh.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This I'll never forget.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SIGHING] Actually, they sent in-- don't forget, Hitler came to power in '33.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are talking of '38 to '39.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they sent in German Nazis to learn from the Austrians how to be radical because they had gotten lax already.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
